imatinib 800 mg/day. The incremental societal cost amounts to EUR 4 250 during 
the lifetime period, or EUR6880 per QALY gained.
CONCLUSION: The results indicate that dasatinib is a cost-effective treatment 
among imatinib-resistant CML patients in Sweden in comparison to imatinib 800 
mg/daily.

