DNA-ligand binding and the force-extension experiments. Comment on "Biophysical 
characterization of DNA binding from single molecule force measurements" by 
Chaurasiya et al.

Vologodskii A(1).

Author information:
(1)Department of Chemistry, New York University, New York, NY 10003, USA. 
